s."],[7529,7579,"The partying rumors,"],[7579,7629,"The partying rumors,"],[7629,7795,"the fake cheating scandals..."],[7916,8054,"God, she probably thinks"],[8054,8195,"I've slept with hundreds of women."],[8591,8816,"Trust me, I'm usually very restrained."],[8908,9079,"Except with you."],[9220,9295,"This is all I want."],[9529,9587,"Just you..."],[9741,9800,"and me."],[9933,9991,"And that's it."]],"11":[[350,575,"I can't believe I just slept with the"],[575,725,"biggest star in Hollywood."],[2612,2679,"Good morning."],[3316,3425,"I know that you were fired from"],[3425,3516,"your job yesterday."],[3566,3616,"Okay?"],[3729,3787,"So..."],[3816,3912,"I just gotta know,"],[3912,4075,"are you in some kind of trouble?"],[4212,4287,"Are you okay? What's..."],[4287,4387,"What's going on?"],[4475,4637,"It's bad enough I slept with Blake."],[4675,4825,"I can't ask him to fix"],[4825,4950,"my problems for me too."],[5062,5125,"Umm..."],[5204,5337,"No, I, I'm not."],[5416,5454,"It..."],[5500,5637,"It's okay, I'll figure it out."],[5762,5812,"Question for you."],[5937,6112,"Why did you offer me that big role?"],[6150,6287,"Cos I can't help but wonder"],[6287,6437,"if maybe it's because you thought"],[6612,6791,"a scandal would bring more press"],[6791,6862,"or something."],[6904,7066,"I offered you the role because"],[7066,7200,"you're talented, Blake."],[7262,7375,"I know you can be so much more than"],[7375,7562,"the heartthrob or the action hero, and..."],[7654,7891,"I know you want more too."],[8050,8137,"Is she just telling me"],[8137,8200,"what I want to hear?"],[8279,8454,"I wish I could believe she's different, but..."],[8487,8641,"every time I trust somebody,"],[8641,8800,"they end up using me to get their"],[8800,8925,"fifteen minutes of fame."],[9054,9112,"Okay."],[9254,9375,"So I got to know,"],[9375,9637,"what do you want from all this?"],[9837,9950,"As much as I shouldn't,"],[9950,10041,"I want Blake."],[10104,10312,"But am I just another notch"],[10312,10412,"in